Deploy Database Firewall with OpenDAM
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Install and configure a database activity monitoring system
Implement database access logging and monitoring
Create Python scripts to analyze database activity patterns
Build automated alerting systems for suspicious database access
Configure firewall rules to protect database communications
