Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Monitor script fails to connect to database

Solution: Verify MySQL credentials in config file
Check MySQL service status: sudo systemctl status mysql
Test connection: mysql -u root -p
Issue: No logs appearing in activity.log

Solution: Check file permissions: ls -l /opt/opendam/logs/
Verify monitor script is running: ps aux | grep opendam
Check for errors: tail -f /opt/opendam/logs/activity.log
Issue: Alerts not generating

Solution: Verify alert thresholds in configuration
Check alert log exists: ls -l /opt/opendam/logs/alerts.log
Test with intentional suspicious activity
